Field, Appellant, v. Burr Brewing Co., Respondent. {Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 12, 1890.) Appeal from city court, general term.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

F. Kurzman, for appellant. B. W. Traitel, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment reversed, new trial ordered, costs to abide the -event.
